messages.speech:
Causes of Diabetes:

1. There’s a history of diabetes in your family
2. You’re middle-aged or older
3. You’re overweight or obese
4. You’re middle-aged and have high blood pressure (hypertension)
5. You’ve given birth to a child weighing more than 4.5kg, was diagnosed with gestational diabetes or have/had polycystic ovarian syndrome (PCOS)
